Or let us know what you thought about the demo?</p>\n   885→            </div>\n   886→        </div>\n   887→        <div class=\"row\">\n   888→            <div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2\">\n   889→                <form>\n   890→                    <div class=\"form-group col-md-6\">\n   891→                        <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Name\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"name\">\n   892→                    </div>\n   893→                    <div class=\"form-group col-md-6\">\n   894→                        <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Email\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"email\">\n   895→                    </div>\n   896→                    <div class=\"form-group col-xs-12\">\n   897→                        <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Subject\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"subject\">\n   898→                    </div>\n   899→                    <div class=\"form-group col-xs-12\">\n   900→                        <textarea class=\"form-control\" placeholder=\"How can we help you?\" rows=\"6\" id=\"message\"></textarea>\n   901→                    </div>\n   902→                    <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-default\">Submit</button>\n   903→                </form>\n   904→            </div>\n   905→        </div>\n   906→        <div class=\"row contact-boxes\">\n   907→            <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\n   908→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"400ms\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   909→                    <i class=\"fa fa-map-marker\"></i>\n   910→                    <h6>Visit With Us</h6>\n   911→                    <p><a href=\"https://quarkus.io\">Quarkus.io</a></p>\n   912→                </div>\n   913→            </div>\n   914→            <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\n   915→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"800ms\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   916→                    <i class=\"fa fa-phone\"></i>\n   917→                    <h6>Get In Touch</h6>\n   918→                    <p><a href=\"https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com\" >Quarkus Zulip Chat</a></p>\n   919→                    <p><a href=\"https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/quarkus-dev\">Google Groups</a></p>\n   920→                </div>\n   921→            </div>\n   922→            <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\n   923→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1.2s\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   924→                    <i class=\"fa fa-clock-o\"></i>\n   925→                    <h6>Hours of Operation</h6>\n   926→                    <p>Monday-Friday: 9am-7pm<br />\n   927→                        Saturday &amp; Sunday: 8am-8pm\n   928→                    </p>\n   929→                </div>\n   930→            </div>\n   931→        </div>\n   932→    </div>\n   933→</section>\n   934→<section class=\"footer\">\n   935→    <div class=\"container\">\n   936→        <div class=\"row\">\n   937→            <div class=\"col-xs-12\">\n   938→                <ul class=\"list-inline text-center margin-bottom\">\n   939→                    <li><a href=\"\"><i class=\"fa fa-facebook\"></i></a></li>\n   940→                    <li><a href=\"\"><i class=\"fa fa-twitter\"></i></a></li>\n   941→                    <li><a href=\"\"><i class=\"fa fa-linkedin\"></i></a></li>\n   942→                    <li><a href=\"\"><i class=\"fa fa-behance\"></i></a></li>\n   943→                </ul>\n   944→                <p class=\"text-center\">© 2018 <a href=\"http://hh-themes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">HH Themes</a></p>\n   945→                <!-- Please do not remove the backlink to us unless you have purchased a license. It is part of the license conditions. Thanks for understanding :) -->\n   946→            </div>\n   947→        </div>\n   948→    </div>\n   949→    <div id=\"back-to-top\"><i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-up\"></i></div>\n   950→</section>\n   951→<div class=\".d-none\"></div>\n   952→<appvalues id=\"appvalues\"\n   953→           data-store-id=\"{storeId}\"\n   954→           data-stream-url=\"{streamUrl}\"\n   955→/>\n   956→<!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap's JavaScript plugins) -->\n   957→<script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n   958→<!-- Include all compiled plugins (below), or include individual files as needed -->\n   959→<script src=\"js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js\"></script>\n   960→<script src=\"js/jquery.matchHeight.js\"></script>\n   961→<script src=\"js/jquery.cookie.js\"></script>\n   962→<script src=\"js/custom.js\"></script>\n   963→<script src=\"js/cafe.js\"></script>\n   964→<script src=\"js/wow.js\"></script>\n   965→<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ekko-lightbox/5.3.0/ekko-lightbox.js\"></script>\n   966→<script src=\"js/toastr.js\"></script>\n   967→<script>\n   968→    new WOW().init();\n   969→</script>\n   970→<script>\n   971→    $(document).on('click', '[data-toggle=\"lightbox\"]', function(event) {\n   972→        event.preventDefault();\n   973→        $(this).ekkoLightbox();\n   974→    });\n   975→</script>\n   976→\n   977→\n   978→</body>\n   979→</html>\n   980→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fccccfb6-6c3c-4161-b41c-50ffcb4f1374","uuid":"456f125e-6e11-4784-8b83-dc49a87a55a8"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01YMvFEDkyHJiYT2Y7uAYeVb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the codebase. Let me plan and execute the migration. This is a Quarkus coffee shop application that uses:\n\n1. **Quarkus-specific features**: Panache ORM, Vert.x event bus, ConsumeEvent, SmallRye reactive messaging (Kafka), Qute templating, MicroProfile Config\n2. **Jakarta EE features already in use**: `jakarta.persistence.*`, `jakarta.inject.*`, `jakarta.ws.rs.*`, `jakarta.enterprise.*`, `jakarta.transaction.*`\n\nThe migration strategy: Convert to a standalone Jakarta EE application using **Open Liberty** as the runtime, which provides full Jakarta EE 10 support. I'll replace Quarkus-specific features with pure Jakarta EE equivalents:\n- Panache -> standard JPA EntityManager\n- Vert.x EventBus -> CDI Events\n- SmallRye Kafka -> Remove Kafka (simplify to in-process)  \n- Qute templates -> simple JSP/static HTML\n- MicroProfile Config -> MicroProfile Config (Liberty supports this)"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":517,"cache_creation_input_tokens":19145,"cache_read_input_tokens":71085,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":19145,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":638},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fccccfb6-6c3c-4161-b41c-50ffcb4f1374","uuid":"68fdcb26-03a1-4b0c-b96d-170bb0dcefac"}
